  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of hypothermic machine perfusion of livers to standard of care (static cold
      storage).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, randomized, multi-center study to show safe and effective use of whole liver
      preservation via hypothermic machine perfusion (HMP) as compared to livers preserved by
      static cold storage.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
